We developed our first model in 2015, the inspiration of our trademark WOODEN.CITYWith the development of new models due to our growing experience has helped us move forward with our ideas. Write to us: woodencity.startup@gmail.comIn order to develop, create and manufacture our 3D wooden construction sets we use high-precision laser equipment.Each produced model is tested by our experts.WOODEN.CITY construction sets have been thoroughly designed and tested each set includes detailed step-by-step instructions.Main characteristics of WOODEN.CITY 3D puzzles:Material – environmentally friendly birch plywood;Rotates with help of a rubber motor;Assembly does not require glue;Packaging – wooden box;Recommended for the children aged 14 years old.     Models WOODEN.CITY are a great present for any occasion!   One of the oldest attractions, known to everyone since childhood, is “FERRIS WHEEL”.More than 120 years ago the project of the wheel with cabins for observation seemed impossible. But a young engineer-creator believed in his dream.Do you want to try yourself as innovator and plunge into the atmosphere of the previous century?Once you've opened the wooden box and breathed in the air smelling like the carpenter's workshop, the mechanical model “FERRIS WHEEL” will take over your imagination while helping to develop logical thinking.“WOODEN.CITY” 3D puzzle is an exciting construction set with open mechanism. The assembly does not require any glue. Press the parts and assemble in accordance with the instructions.Several turns of the key and the rubber motor of “FERRIS WHEEL” is started! It triggers off the gears, among which there is a flywheel and a real planet gear. The operating time is 1 minute. The trigger lever on the right side can be used to stop the movement of the wheel.At the bottom of the patterned stand there is a secret coin boxSecret coin box Construction set features:Model size L*B*H, mm - 220*260*322;Packing size, mm - 355*240*51;Brutto, kg - 2,350;It is started with a special key;Rotates with help of the rubber motor;The operating time from one start is 1 minute;There is a trigger lever;Assembly does not require any glue;Number of the parts - 429;Assembly time - 8 hours. Green meadow, birds in the blue sky and “MILL” is a traditional European landscape.As soon as you open a brand wooden box smelling as a carpenter's workshop, the mechanical model “MILL” will take you imagination.Several turns of the key and the rubber motor of “MILL” is started! It triggers off the gears, among which there is a flywheel.The operating time from one start is 1 minute. On the left there is a trigger lever used to stop movement of the MILL.But wait, there is more! At the bottom of the patterned stand there is a secret coin box.Construction set features:Model size L*B*H, mm - 327*373*135;Packing size, mm - 355*240*40;Brutto, kg - 1,600;It is started with a special key;Rotates with help of the rubber motor;The operating time from one start is 1 minute;There is a trigger lever;Assembly does not require any glue;Number of the parts - 222;Assembly time - 7 hours. Is it a mechanical watch? Wrong. It is the model of “KINETIC PICTURE”! Start the mechanism with a special key and the optical illusion will take your imagination!Open the brand wooden box and after two or three fascinating evenings of leisure you will surprise you guests with an unusual moving picture.Several turns of the key and the rubber motor of the “KINETIC PICTURE” is started!It triggers off the gears. You may observe the rotation process.With help of the trigger lever on the right you may regulate the tension of the rubber band and rotation speed.Construction set features:Model size L*B*H, mm - 340*224*62;Packing size, mm - 355*240*40;Brutto, kg - 1,250;It is started with a special key;Rotates with help of the rubber motor;The operating time from one start is 1 minute;There is a trigger lever;Assembly does not require any glue;Number of the parts - 185;Assembly time – 6 hours.  
The real world of illusions on your wall! A find for modern design and retro style in the interior. "MECHANICAL PICTURE" 3D puzzle by “WOODEN.CITY” with an open mechanism.

Open the brand wooden box and after two or three fascinating evenings of leisure you will surprise you guests with an unusual moving picture.

"WOODEN.CITY" 3D puzzle is a construction set made of environmentally friendly materials with an open mechanism. The assembly dos not require any glue. Press the parts from the boards and assemble according to the instructions.
Several turns of the key and the rubber motor of the “MECHANICAL PICTURE " is started! It triggers off the gears. You may observe the whole rotation process. With help of the trigger lever on the right, it is possible to adjust the tightness of the rubber band and speed of rotation of the mechanism. The operating time from one start is 1 minute. The trigger lever is on the right.

The «MECHANICAL PICTURE» by "WOODEN.CITY" is a real find for those who appreciate beauty and love science.

Construction set features
Brand – Wooden city;
Packaging – a wooden box;
Material – environmentally friendly birch plywood, rubber bands;
It is started with a key;
There are two disks rotating with different speeds;
Rotates with help of a rubber motor;
The operating time from one start is 1 minute;
Tension of the rubber band is adjustable;
There is a trigger lever;
A special hook is attached to hang the picture on the wall;
Assembly does not require any glue;
Number of the parts – 245 on 5 sheets
Spare parts – 23
Assembly time – 8 hours.
Recommended for the children aged 14 years old.
 Today, we represent "4x4", as an expensive off-the-road vehicle for brutal men. During the Second World War, the American company Willys started production of the Willys MB automobile. It went down in history as a reliable, manoeuvrable and functional vehicle. It was a "technical breakthrough". There was a real "war of engines". Overcoming of obstacles, road dust and risk! You have a real adventure in your hands!4x4​ model has:  - an internal combustion engine with moving pistons and a release lever at the rear of the car; - a ratchet mechanism; - a lever for switching the direction of travel; - three moving pedals (which are resiliently pressed with an additional rubber band); - at the rear of the model there is a trailing arm intended for the trailer; - four-wheel drive transmission, independent suspension on both axles; - removable shovel, axe and canister; - rear-view mirror; - drive of the model has joints and semi-axles with crossings like a real automobile.The automobile model can drive up to 2 meters. After assembly, you need to set the position of the lever forward or backward, set the locking lever in the stop position, start the model with a key and lower the lever (the key is located in the spare wheel). The front wheels are steered. The hood is opened and fixed by two locks, and the windshield tilts."WOODEN.CITY" 3D puzzle is a construction set made of environmentally friendly materials with an open mechanism. The assembly does not require any glue. Press the parts and assemble in accordance with the instructions."WOODEN.CITY" 4x4 is a real find for those who are fond of history and like adventure.Construction set featuresBrand – Wooden city;Packing – wooden box;Material – environmentally friendly birch plywood, rubber bands;Length of the path – 2 meters;The model moves back and forth;Independent suspension;It is started with a special key;The assembly does not require any glue;Number of the parts – 520 on 9 sheets;Assembly time – 12 hours.Recommended for the children aged 14 years old. Have you been to London earlier? You have a unique opportunity to plunge into the atmosphere of conservative London, creating a unique Double Decker.It has a rubber motor, which may be easily started with a key.LONDON BUS has two levels of speed and directions of movement.Construction set features:Model size L*B*H, mm - 232*70*115;Packing size, mm - 355*240*40;Brutto, kg - 1,090;It is started with a special key;Rotates with help of the rubber motor;The length of the path from one started is 4 meters;There are two control levers (speed and direction);Assembly does not require any glue;Number of the parts - 216;Assembly time - 6 hours. Would you like to construct your own airplane for less than 2 hours?Try our Biplane. It has original rubber motor with a controlled acceleration.   Construction set features:Model size L*B*H, mm - 161*140*88;Packing size, mm - 240*175*28 ;Brutto, kg - 0,310;Rotates with help of the rubber motor;The length of the path from one started is 0,5 meters;Assembly does not require any glue;Number of the parts - 63;Assembly time - 2 hours. Chariots were used for warfighting by a number of armies –Egyptian, Greek, Roman, Assyrian and Persian. The warriors felt themselves mobile shock flight, which blazed through everything alive on this unique vehicle.They were always ahead or acted on the flank of the infantry. Such military lights destroyed the enemies in a moment, so that the following infantry just dealt the final blow to those, who managed to escape the chariot. The technique is rude, but efficient. In any case, power of the ancient army was judged by a number of used chariots.CHARIOT DA VINCIDa Vinci scythed chariot is a war chariot with scythe blades mounted on each side, employed in ancient times. The blades extended horizontally to each side of the wheels. Scythed chariot would plow through infantry lines cutting combatants in.CHARIOT DA VINCI CHARIOT DA VINCIConstruction set features CHARIOT DA VINCI:Model size L*B*H, mm - 230*107*104;Packing size, mm - 240*175*28;Brutto, kg - 0,300;Rotates with help of the rubber motor;The length of the path from one started is 1 meter;Assembly does not require any glue;Number of the parts - 74;Assembly time - 2 hours.ROMAN CHARIOTRoman chariot is a war chariot employed and operated by Roman warriors in ancient times. This historically accurate Wooden City 3-D wooden puzzle with the rubber band engine was created just for you.ROMAN CHARIOTROMAN CHARIOTConstruction set features ROMAN CHARIOT:Model size L*B*H, mm - 220*55*130;Packing size, mm - 240*175*28;Brutto, kg - 0,300;Rotates with help of the rubber motor;The length of the path from one started is 1 meter;Assembly does not require any glue;Number of the parts - 69;Assembly time - 2 hours. Set of three funny trinkets, which may be assembled together by yourself: Spinning Top and two different key chains.To each parcel free of charge.Construction set features:Model size L*B*H, mm - 106*59*17;Packing size, mm - 106*59*17;Brutto, kg - 0,050;Assembly does not require any glue;Number of the parts - 29;Assembly time - 30 min. The WOODEN.CITY Team:We are a small company consisting of creative people, fond of our business. Our team is not large, but friendly. We have a lot of new ideas, which we want to communicate to you!Vlad, Anton and NadezhdaLeonid and YuriWe developed our first model at the end of 2015, and it became an inspiration for creation of our trademark WOODEN.CITYQuality controlOur growing experience in development of new models has helped us to move forward with our ideas.High-precision laser equipmentWe have our own production with high-precision laser equipment.Finished products All we need now is your support!Why do we need you support?We are a small company in the EU (Poland).With your support, we will be able to create and release new models.We invite you to participate in this process.Risks and challengesWe have small production facility, experience in delivery and international transportation.We guarantee high quality of our products.We have drawn up a well thought-out plan on further actions after completion of the project.We choose the most convenient and reliable means of delivery.Orders for our supporters will be sent from the EU.
